ESET NOD32 Smart Security BUILD: 6.0.316.0
Eset Smart Security description:

ESET Smart Security was designed to be complete solution in the field of computer protection against infiltrations and attacks. Eset Smart Security offers more than just a sum of its parts, it is synergy that matters most. If all components are used simultaneously, the effectiveness of the whole program is multiplied. ESET Smart Security unifies all its functions to create a complex security solution.

Installation Instructions:
Code:
1- Install the NOD32 with the version you want (32 Bit or 64 Bit);
2- Right click on the taskbar NOD32 icon;
3- Deactivate firewall protection and normal protection;
4- Open the NOD32 Licence updater setup and install in the ESET's Directory;
5- Open the License Updater and wait untill it finds a valid license;
6- Update NOD32 and check the license status;
7- Enable all the protections again;

